dc_title_s: Electric Transmission Lines: United States, Summer 2014
dc_description_s: This line shapefile provides the location, current and previous owners, kilovolts of power, operational status, and other infomation about electric transmission lines in the United States. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Summer Quarter update (Update 1016). This layer can be used to locate electric transmission lines in the United States. Hart Energy Publishing (2016). Electric Transmission Lines: United States, Summer 2014. Hart Energy Publishing. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/sd478sb7334. This release is intended to replace all previous datasets. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
